room_title: Escape room "Paradise?" by The Cryptic Room in Omaha
room_address: 523 S Main St Council Bluffs, IA 51503
room_description:
You have inherited Paradise from your Great Aunt Myrtle. She and Uncle Ed loved the island and their little Tiki bar, but they left a warning - when the god and goddess on the island get restless, the volcano can become very destructive.

Can the chosen one be found to honor the gods before you and Paradise are lost forever?
